{"tid":479894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗仔勁驚個枕頭 會唔會果味野","createTime":"2017-11-25T15:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T17:45:12.000Z","uid":97737,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3b7a789e4fa50c2b759ffecd569beb50d4c4df","tid":479894,"uid":97737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"話說我有隻3個月大嘅貴婦狗仔。<br />\n    有一日，我翻到屋企，佢冇如常咁撲出黎我度，而係企上左係一張櫈仔上面好驚咁。見到我翻黎，就企係我腳邊吠向佢個『狗鬥』。我望過去，見到原本擺左係『狗鬥』上面個窗台嘅一個小枕頭跌左落佢個『狗鬥』度。然後得知佢係驚個枕頭，我調教一陣之後佢就唔驚喇，仲玩起個枕頭。<br />\n    但係之後，佢會間唔鍾都驚個枕頭，唔敢埋去，係咁吠。<br />\n    聽講狗對果味野好敏感，會唔會係呢?定係我諗多左?"},{"pid":"75cb96b388170274e02ef82d8501a43ec526d9d3","tid":479894,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede65fa46df0385e572bd14019dde388d89c2806","tid":479894,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"可能係臭味野"},{"pid":"b668354cb593437684243d02617d4fef1d0caf7d","tid":479894,"uid":97737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能係臭味野</blockquote><br />\n個枕頭係有d味 但係又點解會時驚時唔驚嘅?"},{"pid":"04a51ee7a881fd7a0b64c4338bba11a3912f2921","tid":479894,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"你揾個傳心師問吓"},{"pid":"d23f7e6fc207219a226650ce83fd770f699b4fcd","tid":479894,"uid":52503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能係臭味野</blockquote><br />\n個枕頭係有d味 但係又點解會時驚時唔驚嘅?</blockquote><br />\n洗頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9992888c02013513a622a6a579e760ed9b2086","tid":479894,"uid":97737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能係臭味野</blockquote><br />\n個枕頭係有d味 但係又點解會時驚時唔驚嘅?</blockquote><br />\n洗頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個枕頭唔係我ga  係佢『狗鬥』送"},{"pid":"d392035651a9e624bbb2e6a0a0e3a499398f6cbe","tid":479894,"uid":18241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:40:54.000Z","msg":"2018年仲咁多垃圾迷信撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b83096fa528c0ef894c51c54663d80ed486106a","tid":479894,"uid":123577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇死人咩"}]}